      "cooked": "<ul>\n<li>C’jane riffs?</li>\n<li>Si c’jane riffs? Riffs jane ato grupimet e notave/kordave qe te saldohen ne tru e nuk ndryshken gjer sa te  vdesesh. Jane shkaku qe ti ben sikur di ti biesh kitarres duke ngjitur gishtin e madh me ate tregues e duke i ferkuar xhinset nen xhep.</li>\n<li>Shembuj?<br>\n-Shembuj, posi!</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"lazyYT\" data-youtube-id=\"O8RhZDGLEXM\" data-youtube-title=\"FLEETWOOD MAC - Oh Well  (1969 UK TV Performance) ~ HIGH QUALITY HQ ~\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"270\" data-parameters=\"feature=oembed&amp;wmode=opaque\"></div><br>\n<div class=\"lazyYT\" data-youtube-id=\"VikyxJoBF2k\" data-youtube-title=\"Haim - Oh Well live at T in the Park 2014\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"270\" data-parameters=\"feature=oembed&amp;wmode=opaque\"></div>\n<ul>\n<li>Shembuj pa fund!</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"lazyYT\" data-youtube-id=\"G4pp02_GN9A\" data-youtube-title=\"John Lee Hooker Boogie Chillen original 1948 version\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"270\" data-parameters=\"feature=oembed&amp;wmode=opaque\"></div><br>\n<div class=\"lazyYT\" data-youtube-id=\"fHEmDLQKrrk\" data-youtube-title=\"Link Wray - Rumble - 11/19/1974 - Winterland (Official)\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"270\" data-parameters=\"feature=oembed&amp;wmode=opaque\"></div><br>\n<div class=\"lazyYT\" data-youtube-id=\"X70VMrH3yBg\" data-youtube-title=\"John Lee Hooker - Boom Boom [HQ]\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"270\" data-parameters=\"feature=oembed&amp;wmode=opaque\"></div><br>\n<div class=\"lazyYT\" data-youtube-id=\"zt51rITH3EA\" data-youtube-title=\"Cream - Sunshine Of Your Love (HD)\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"270\" data-parameters=\"feature=oembed&amp;wmode=opaque\"></div><br>\n<div class=\"lazyYT\" data-youtube-id=\"PE9HvSdcaL4\" data-youtube-title=\"Cream Crossroads\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"270\" data-parameters=\"feature=oembed&amp;wmode=opaque\"></div><br>\n<div class=\"lazyYT\" data-youtube-id=\"egMWlD3fLJ